{"tid":630684,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"準唔準試過就知","createTime":"2018-04-15T20:02:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-19T14:54:55.000Z","uid":127241,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e59509c756704bebb68e99eaebc260e101facf8e","tid":630684,"uid":127241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T20:02:20.000Z","msg":"慈善奇門占又登陸平台<br />\n多謝咁多位巴絲支持 <br />\n期待佐咁耐 規矩照舊<br />\n問事 占卜規則:<br />\n低B 戇居 無聊問題 投機賭博問題等等一律不占<br />\n簡單一事一占答完請做返一件善事回饋社會就可以 只作簡單占卜，詳細解答須酌情收取隨喜酬勞 <br />\n如果要再占請等下次post或等冇人問時再占 緊急解答須酌情收取隨喜酬勞<br />\n<br />\n短時間內可能未咁快回覆到各位<br />\n希望問事者見諒<br />\n有野問就加我ig 之後direct我 <br />\nig：the_miracle_fighters<br />\n如果ig搵我，講明係連登見到add我"},{"pid":"aab0c3c37063272f10e0445c9d7bef1ce14e082e","tid":630684,"uid":2419,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T20:23:13.000Z","msg":"詳細解答須酌情收取隨喜酬勞 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n憑乜野？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fef9ad1d29afee36b607c40a55449c8db03290c0","tid":630684,"uid":21844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T20:30:09.000Z","msg":"幫我占卜下愛情同事業運<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d01903df21586e5316d7ff216eddeaf30a65ae3","tid":630684,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aab0c3c37063272f10e0445c9d7bef1ce14e082e","tid":630684,"uid":2